name: Stone Revival
description:
Musical freedom is Stone Revival's game.

With sounds ranging from heavy hard rock, swamp blues, breakneck funk and psychedelic jams, the band take pride in diversity and pushing the boundaries of what rock is about.

Stone Revival are a 3 piece band with a mission not dissimiliar to other power trio's like;
The Experience, ZZ Top and Stevie Ray Vaughan & Double Trouble, although with a completely reworked take on the mould.

With Matty on drums, Henry on bass and Bud on guitar & vocals, the band's live show is sure to get down on anyone with a heartbeat. If you don't have one, they'll revive it !

Power Trio from 
Melbourne, Australia
8 songs with full colour 8 page booklet.
